comments:
I was pretty bad to start with, but found the paired task easier. I did pick up the prefix being linked with a shape quite early on(e.g. zeti being the spiky one, wop being the circle). It took a bit longer to notice the suffix being the colour (e being blue). Although I picked both these things up, it took a while to actually get them to stick in my mind.

I did not think to use paper, although I'm sure that would have helped. The person I was partned with seemed to have a better knowledge of the language than me, so I think that helped solidify my knowledge, and helped us perform well overall.
